      "blocks": {
        "faq-1": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Is Baudie a deodorant?",
            "answer": "<p>No. Baudie is not a deodorant and does not replace one. It works before deodorant to stop odor at the source and create the perfect base for your deo to shine.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq-2": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How do I use it?",
            "answer": "<p>Spray Baudie onto clean, dry underarms before applying your deodorant. Let it dry for a moment, then layer your favorite deo on top.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq-3": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Why do I need a pre-deodorant?",
            "answer": "<p>Deodorant masks odor — Baudie eliminates it at the source. By removing odor-causing bacteria first, your deodorant works better and lasts longer.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq-4": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What does \"odor-eliminating bacterial technology\" mean?",
            "answer": "<p>It means Baudie uses gentle AHAs and plant-powered actives to target and neutralize the specific bacteria that cause body odor, creating an environment where they can't thrive.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq-5": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Will the enhancer scent mix with my deodorant or perfume?",
            "answer": "<p>Baudie's scent is light and designed to complement — not compete with — your deodorant or fragrance. It fades quickly, leaving a clean base.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq-6": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Can I use Baudie without deodorant?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes! Baudie works on its own to reduce odor-causing bacteria. On lighter days, it may be all you need.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq-7": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Can I use it before workouts?",
            "answer": "<p>Absolutely. Spraying Baudie before a workout gives you an extra layer of freshness when you need it most.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq-8": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Is it suitable for sensitive skin?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes. Baudie is formulated with gentle, skin-friendly ingredients and is free from harsh chemicals. It's designed to work with your skin, not against it.</p>"
